ded the DNS records to your domain settings automatically.","provider.flow.godaddy.cta.sentence_3":"Double check that you pasted the correct TXT value in the <textbutton>previous step</textbutton>","intro.not_sure.description":"Your provider is the site you purchased your business email from. If you\u2019re unsure of the provider\u2019s name, try searching your email for key terms like \u201cbusiness email\u201d \u201cmailbox\u201d or \u201cinvoice\u201d to find a purchase receipt.","provider.flow.microsoft_365.cta.sentence_3":"Double check that you pasted the correct TXT value in the <textbutton>previous step</textbutton>","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.content.sentence_5":"Find the section that matches the record type (e.g. <bold>A, CNAME, TXT</bold>, etc.)","provider.flow.godaddy.card_1.title":"1. Add your domain to {providerName}","provider.flow.godaddy_microsoft_365.card_2.content.sentence_1":"Go through the <bold>\\"1. Select domain,\\" \\"2. Create account,\\" \\"3. Wait for domain verification info\\"</bold> steps until you reach step <bold>\\"4. Verify domain\\"</bold> where you\'ll get the option to <bold>\\"Choose DNS Provider\\"</bold>","provider.flow.table.column_title.ttl":"TTL","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.title":"2. Copy and paste your TXT value ","provider.flow.microsoft_365.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then hit <bold>\u201c{command}\u201d</bold> again","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.content.sentence_4":"Note: If you\u2019ve already added your domain, choose {domainName} and then hit <bold>\u201cStart setup.\u201d</bold>","intro.providers.none.value":"None","provider.flow.other.card_3.content.sentence_2":"Head back to your email provider and copy the record details","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.content.sentence_1":"Choose the first option <bold>\u201cAdd a TXT record to the domain\u2019s DNS records\u201d</bold> and then <bold>\u201cContinue\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.tier2.cta.sentence_3":"Double check that you pasted the correct DNS records in the <textbutton>previous step</textbutton>","provider.flow.tier2.card_3.content.sentence_2":"To finish setup, check that your domain is successfully connected to your email at {providerName}. <div>Note that it might take about 5 minutes for your domain settings to update.</div>","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_3.title":"3. Finish setup at Google","provider.flow.godaddy.card_1.content.sentence_2":"Find the <bold>\u201cEmail & Office\u201d</bold> section and choose <bold>\u201cSet up\u201d</bold> to begin connecting your business email","provider.flow.google_workspace.cta.sentence_3":"Double check that you pasted the correct TXT value in the <textbutton>previous step</textbutton>","provider.flow.other.card_2.title":"2. Get your DNS records from your email provider","provider.flow.google_workspace.command":"Protect Domain","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_1.content.sentence_3":"Choose <bold>\u201cVerify domain\u201d</bold> next to your domain to begin connecting your business email","intro.providers.none":"None","provider.flow.table.row.hour":"{count} Hour","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.cta":"<bold>Note:</bold> Paste all the record details from {providerName} like <bold>Name/Host, Value, TTL, Priority,</bold> etc.","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.tooltip":"The TXT value begins with \u201cMS=ms\\" or \\"D\u201d","provider.flow.microsoft_365.command":"Try Again","intro.not_sure.cta":"Not sure who your email provider is?","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_3.content.sentence_1":"Head back to Google and choose <bold>\u201cProtect Domain\u201d</bold> or <bold>\u201cVerify My Domain\u201d</bold> to finish setup","provider.flow.other.cta.sentence_3":"Double check that you pasted the correct DNS records in the <textbutton>previous step</textbutton>","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.title":"2. Update your domain settings at Wix","intro.next.button":"Next","provider.flow.cta.title":"Is {providerName} unable to verify your domain?","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.content.sentence_6":"Choose <bold>\u201cAdd Record\u201d</bold> paste the record\u2019s details in the relevant fields, and then hit <bold>\u201cSave\u201d</bold> to update your settings","intro.dropdown.placeholder":"Add or choose your email provider","provider.flow.godaddy.card_1.cta.sentence_1":"Can\u2019t find the My Products page?","provider.flow.other.card_4.title":"4. Verify your domain and finish setup at your email provider","provider.flow.godaddy.card_3.content.sentence_1":"Head back to {providerName}. You\'ll then be asked to add more DNS records to your domain, but you don\'t need to do anything because Wix already added them automatically to your domain settings. ","provider.flow.other.card_2.content.sentence_2":"Your provider\u2019s DNS records will look something like this:","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.content.sentence_1":"Go to the <textbutton>Domains page</textbutton> at Microsoft 365 and log in","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_3.content.sentence_1":"Head back to Microsoft and click <bold>\u201cVerify\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.title":"1. Add your domain to Microsoft 365","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.cta.sentence_2":"Head to the Microsoft 365 admin center and open the side menu. Under <bold>\u201cShow All\u201d</bold> go to <bold>\u201cSettings\u201d</bold> and choose <bold>\u201cDomains.\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_3.content.sentence_4":"You\u2019ll know you\u2019re finished with setup when you get a message from Microsoft 365 that <bold>\u201cDomain setup is complete.\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.content.sentence_1":"Go through the <bold>\\"1. Select domain,\\" \\"2. Create account,\\"</bold> steps until you reach step <bold>\\"3. Validate domain\\"</bold> where you\u2019ll see a list of DNS records","provider.flow.cta.sentence_4":"Note: In rare cases, it may take up to an hour for your domain settings to update.","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.validation.message":"To save your value, make sure it begins with \u201dMS=ms\u201d or \u201dD\u201d","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.content.cta":"You\u2019ll need to add your DNS records from {providerName} to your domain settings at Wix. \\n<bold>Some of the records were already added automatically:</bold>","provider.flow.godaddy.card_1.content.sentence_3":"Add your domain name <bold>{domainName}</bold> and then continue to the next step at {providerName}","provider.flow.other.card_1.content.sentence_3":"Add your domain <bold>{domainName}</bold> to begin setting up your email. <div>If you\u2019ve already added it, find your domain name and begin setup.</div>","provider.flow.tier2.card_1.content.sentence_1":"Log in to your {providerName} account","provider.flow.cta.sentence_1":"If your domain is not verified in 5 minutes:","provider.flow.table.row.cta":"Auto added","provider.flow.godaddy.card_1.cta.sentence_2":"Log in to your {providerName} account, open the top right menu, and choose <bold>\u201cMy Products\u201d</bold> under the <bold>\u201cAccount\u201d</bold> section","provider.flow.table.column_title.name_host":"Name/Host","provider.flow.tier2.card_3.content.sentence_1":"Once you\u2019ve added your records at Wix, head back to {providerName}","intro.providers.other.value":"Other","error.message.subtitle":"Try waiting a few more moments and then refresh the page.","provider.flow.continue.button":"Continue","provider.flow.other.card_3.cta":"<bold>Note:</bold> Paste all the record details from {providerName} like <bold>Name/Host, Value, TTL, Priority,</bold> etc.","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_1.tooltip":"\u201cVerify domain\u201d might appear as \u201cProtect your domain.\u201d","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.content.sentence_2":"Copy only the <bold>TXT value</bold> and come back here","provider.flow.godaddy.dropdown.placeholder":"MS=msxxxxxxxx or Dxxxxxxx","provider.flow.other.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then try checking if the domain was successfully connected","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.content.cta":"You\u2019ll need to add your DNS records from {providerName} to your domain settings at Wix. \\n<bold>Some of the records were already added automatically:</bold>","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.content.sentence_1":"You\u2019ll need to add your DNS records from {providerName} to your domain settings at Wix. \\nSome of the records were already added automatically:","provider.flow.godaddy.card_3.content.sentence_2":"To finish setup, hit <bold>\u201cCheck My Settings\u201d</bold> at the bottom of the page. You\u2019ll know you\u2019re done with setup once you get a message from GoDaddy that <bold>\u201cYour email\u2019s ready to use!\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.tier2.card_1.content.sentence_4":"Find the DNS records provided by {providerName} (e.g. <bold>MX, TXT, CNAME</bold>, etc.) <div>Once you get them, keep this page open and come back here.</div>","provider.flow.other.card_3.content.sentence_3":"Go to your domain\'s <textbutton>Manage DNS Records</textbutton> page at Wix","provider.flow.tier2.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then try verifying your domain again","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_1.content.sentence_1":"Head to the <textbutton>Google admin console</textbutton> and log in to your dashboard","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.save_failed.cta":"Try to save your value again or refresh the page","provider.flow.table.column_title.value":"Value","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.content.sentence_2":"At this step, copy only the first <bold>\u201cTXT value\u201d</bold> and come back here"}')},2993:(e,t,o)=>{var n=o(71607),r=o(53852);e.exports=function(e,t){return null!=e&&r(e,t,n)}},3111:e=>{e.exports=function(e,t){var o=e.length;for(e.sort(t);o--;)e[o]=e[o].value;return e}},3482:(e,t,o)=>{"use strict";o.d(t,{O:()=>n});const n=e=>null!=e},3803:(e,t,o)=>{var n=o(46015),r=o(26642),a=o(83572),i=Math.max,s=Math.min;e.exports=function(e,t,o){var l,c,d,u,p,m,h=0,f=!1,g=!1,v=!0;if("function"!=typeof e)throw 