s":"Show Less","provider.flow.done.button":"Done","provider.flow.other.card_1.content.sentence_2":"Go to your email settings page <div>This page might be called \u201cManage Email,\u201d \u201cEmail DNS Settings\u201d or \u201cEmail DNS Management.\u201d</div>","intro.subtitle":"Where did you purchase your business email?","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_3.content.sentence_2":"It might take up to 5 minutes for Google to verify your domain. Once setup is complete, you\u2019ll get a message that your domain is protected. You\u2019ll also be able to check that your domain is verified on the <bold>Manage domains</bold> page at Google.","provider.flow.other.card_1.title":"1. Add your domain to your email provider","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.content.sentence_3":"Add your domain name <bold>{domainName}</bold> and then choose <bold>\u201cUse This Domain\u201d</bold>","error.message.title":"This page isn\u2019t loading because of a problem on our end","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.content.sentence_3":"Head back to {providerName} and copy the record details","wizard.cta":"Having trouble? Get more detailed instuctions on <textbutton>connecting an email purchased outside Wix</textbutton>.","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.tooltip":"The TXT value begins with \u201cMS=ms\u201d","provider.flow.tier2.card_1.title":"1. Get your DNS records from {providerName}","provider.flow.microsoft_365.dropdown.placeholder":"MS=msxxxxxxxx","intro.providers.dropdown.not_found":"No match for \\"{inputValue}\\"","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.validation.message":"To save your value, make sure it begins with \u201dGOOGLE-SITE-VERIFICATION=\u201d","provider.flow.table.row.show_all_records":"Show All Records ({count})","provider.flow.your_email_provider":"your email provider","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_1.title":"1. Verify your domain at Google","error.message.cta":"Or, Go Back to Choosing an Email Provider","provider.flow.google_workspace.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few min