onnecting an email purchased outside Wix</textbutton>.","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.tooltip":"The TXT value begins with \u201cMS=ms\u201d","provider.flow.tier2.card_1.title":"1. Get your DNS records from {providerName}","provider.flow.microsoft_365.dropdown.placeholder":"MS=msxxxxxxxx","intro.providers.dropdown.not_found":"No match for \\"{inputValue}\\"","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.validation.message":"To save your value, make sure it begins with \u201dGOOGLE-SITE-VERIFICATION=\u201d","provider.flow.table.row.show_all_records":"Show All Records ({count})","provider.flow.your_email_provider":"your email provider","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_1.title":"1. Verify your domain at Google","error.message.cta":"Or, Go Back to Choosing an Email Provider","provider.flow.google_workspace.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then hit <bold>\u201c{command}\u201d</bold> or <bold>\u201c{command}\u201d</bold> again","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.validation.message":"To save your value, make sure it begins with \u201dMS=ms\u201d","provider.flow.godaddy.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then hit <bold>\u201c{command}\u201d</bold> again","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.cta.sentence_1":"Can\u2019t find the Domains page?","provider.flow.success.card.title":"You\u2019ve set up {domainName} with your {providerName} email","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_3.title":"3. Verify your domain and finish setup at Microsoft 365","provider.flow.start_connecting.button.cta":"To start connecting, choose an email provider","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.content.sentence_1":"Go straight to <bold>\u201cStep 2\u201d</bold> and find your <bold>\u201cTXT record\u201d</bold>","error.message.button":"Refresh Page","provider.flow.other.card_1.content.sentence_1":"Log in to your email provider","provider.flow.table.column_title.type":"Type","provider.flow.tier2.card_3.title":"3. Verify your domain and finish setup at {providerName}","provider.flow.other.card_3.content.sentence_4":"Find the section that matches the record type (e.g. <bold>A, CNAME, TXT</bold>, etc.)","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_3.content.sentence_2":"After clicking <bold>\\"Verify,\\"</bold> choose <bold>\\"Add your own DNS records\\"</bold> and then hit <bold>\u201cContinue\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.godaddy.card_3.title":"3. Finish setup at {providerName}","intro.providers.other":"Other (provider not on the list)","provider.flow.success.card.content":"Head back to {providerName} to continue managing your email. <div>You can view your updated domain settings on the Domains page at Wix.</div>","provider.flow.godaddy_microsoft_365.card_2.content.sentence_2":"At this step, choose Wix as your DNS provider, copy only the first <bold>\u201cTXT value\u201d</bold> and come back here","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.content.sentence_2":"Copy only the <bold>\u201cTXT value\u201d</bold> and come back here","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.tooltip":"The TXT value begins with \u201cGOOGLE-SITE-VERIFICATION\u201d","provider.flow.other.card_2.content.sentence_1":"Your email provider will then give you a list of DNS records (like <bold>MX, TXT, CNAME,</bold> etc.). \\nOnce you get them, keep the page open and come back here.","provider.flow.godaddy.command":"Check My Settings","provider.flow.tier2.card_1.content.sentence_3":"Add your domain <bold>{domainName}</bold> to begin setting up your email <div>If you\u2019ve already added it, find your domain name and begin setup.</div>","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.content.cta":"You\u2019ll need to add your DNS records from {providerName} to your domain settings at Wix. \\n<bold>Some of the records were already added automatically:</bold>","provider.flow.table.row.hour_plural":"{count} Hours","provider.flow.start_connecting.button":"Start Connecting","provider.flow.other.card_3.title":"3. Update your domain settings at Wix","provider.flow.godaddy.card_1.content.sentence_1":"Go to the <textbutton>My Products page</textbutton> at {providerName} and log in","provider.flow.other.card_4.content.sentence_1":"Once you\u2019ve added your records at Wix, head back to your email provider","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_1.content.sentence_2":"Open the side menu. Under <bold>\u201cAccount,\u201d</bold> go to <bold>\u201cDomains\u201d</bold> and choose <bold>\u201cManage domains.\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.save_failed.cta":"Try to save your value again or refresh the page","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.content.sentence_4":"Go to your domain\'s <textbutton>Manage DNS Records</textbutton> page at Wix","provider.flow.other.card_3.content.sentence_1":"You\u2019ll need to add the DNS records from your email provider to your domain settings at Wix. \\nTo add each record:","intro.title":"To connect an email address to your domain <bold>{domainName}</bold>, you\u2019ll need to update your domain settings. This will only take about 5 minutes and you\u2019ll be guided step-by-step.","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.content.sentence_2":"Choose <bold>\u201cAdd Domain\u201d</bold> to begin connecting your business email","provider.flow.dropdown.cta":"Paste the TXT value and save it","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.title":"2. Copy and paste your Microsoft 365 TXT value","provider.flow.tier2.card_1.content.sentence_2":"Go to your email settings page <div>This page might be called \u201cManage Email,\u201d \u201cEmail DNS Settings\u201d or \u201cEmail DNS Management.\u201d</div>","provider.flow.go_to_domains.button":"Go to Domains","provider.flow.other.card_3.content.sentence_5":"Choose <bold>\u201cAdd Record\u201d</bold> paste the record\u2019s details in the relevant fields, and then hit <bold>\u201cSave\u201d</bold> to update your settings","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.title":"2. Copy and paste your TXT value","provider.flow.google_workspace.dropdown.placeholder":"GOOGLE-SITE-VERIFCATION=...","provider.flow.table.column_title.priority":"Priority","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_3.content.sentence_3":"Once you reach the <bold>\u201cAdd DNS records\u201d</bold> page, you can click <bold>\u201cContinue\u201d</bold> and skip this step without doing anything because Wix already added the DNS records to your domain settings automatically.","provider.flow.godaddy.cta.sentence_3":"Double check that you pasted the correct TXT value in the <textbutton>previous step</textbutton>","intro.not_sure.description":"Your provider is the site you purchased your business email from. If you\u2019re unsure of the provider\u2019s name, try searching your email for key terms like \u201cbusiness email\u201d \u201cmailbox\u201d or \u201cinvoice\u201d to find a purchase receipt.","provider.flow.microsoft_365.cta.sentence_3":"Double check that you pasted the correct TXT value in the <textbutton>previous step</textbutton>","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.content.sentence_5":"Find the section that matches the record type (e.g. <bold>A, CNAME, TXT</bold>, etc.)","provider.flow.godaddy.card_1.title":"1. Add your domain to {providerName}","provider.flow.godaddy_microsoft_365.card_2.content.sentence_1":"Go through the <bold>\\"1. Select domain,\\" \\"2. Create account,\\" \\"3. Wait for domain verification info\\"</bold> steps until you reach step <bold>\\"4. Verify domain\\"</bold> where you\'ll get the option to <bold>\\"Choose DNS Provider\\"</bold>","provider.flow.table.column_title.ttl":"TTL","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.title":"2. Copy and paste your TXT value ","provider.flow.microsoft_365.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then hit <bold>\u201c{command}\u201d</bold> again","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_1.content.sentence_4":"Note: If you\u2019ve already added your domain, choose {domainName} and then hit <bold>\u201cStart setup.\u201d</bold>","intro.providers.none.value":"None","provider.flow.other.card_3.content.sentence_2":"Head back to your email provider and copy the record details","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.content.sentenc