ue</bold> and come back here","provider.flow.godaddy.dropdown.placeholder":"MS=msxxxxxxxx or Dxxxxxxx","provider.flow.other.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then try checking if the domain was successfully connected","provider.flow.microsoft_365.card_2.content.cta":"You\u2019ll need to add your DNS records from {providerName} to your domain settings at Wix. \\n<bold>Some of the records were already added automatically:</bold>","provider.flow.tier2.card_2.content.sentence_1":"You\u2019ll need to add your DNS records from {providerName} to your domain settings at Wix. \\nSome of the records were already added automatically:","provider.flow.godaddy.card_3.content.sentence_2":"To finish setup, hit <bold>\u201cCheck My Settings\u201d</bold> at the bottom of the page. You\u2019ll know you\u2019re done with setup once you get a message from GoDaddy that <bold>\u201cYour email\u2019s ready to use!\u201d</bold>","provider.flow.tier2.card_1.content.sentence_4":"Find the DNS records provided by {providerName} (e.g. <bold>MX, TXT, CNAME</bold>, etc.) <div>Once you get them, keep this page open and come back here.</div>","provider.flow.other.card_3.content.sentence_3":"Go to your domain\'s <textbutton>Manage DNS Records</textbutton> page at Wix","provider.flow.tier2.cta.sentence_2":"Wait a few minutes and then try verifying your domain again","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_1.content.sentence_1":"Head to the <textbutton>Google admin console</textbutton> and log in to your dashboard","provider.flow.google_workspace.card_2.save_failed.cta":"Try to save your value again or refresh the page","provider.flow.table.column_title.value":"Value","provider.flow.godaddy.card_2.content.sentence_2":"At this step, copy only the first <bold>\u201cTXT value\u201d</bold> and come back here"}')},90856:(e,t,o)=>{"use strict";var n=o(7183);function r(){}function a(){}a.resetWarningCache=r,e.exports=function(){function e(e,t,o,r,a,i){if(i!==n){var s=new Error("Calling PropTypes validators